  "prompt": "What is the best Instagram followers tracking app?",
  "response": "There are several popular Instagram follower tracking apps that can help you manage your followers and analyze your engagement. Here are some of the best options as of 2023:\n\n1. **Hootsuite**: Offers social media management along with analytics tools that help track followers and engagement metrics.\n\n2. **SocialBlade**: Provides insights into follower growth, engagement rates, and other statistics for Instagram accounts.\n\n3. **Combin**: This app focuses on audience management and growth, helping users track followers, unfollowers, and engagement.\n\n4. **Follower Analyzer for Instagram**: This app provides detailed analytics on followers, unfollowers, and those who don't follow you back.\n\n5. **Iconosquare**: A comprehensive Instagram analytics tool that offers insights into follower demographics, engagement metrics, and content performance.\n\n6. **Analisa.io**: Offers in-depth analytics for Instagram profiles, including follower growth, engagement metrics, and hashtag performance.\n\nWhen choosing an app, consider what features are most important to you, such as tracking unfollowers, engagement metrics, or audience demographics, as well as ease of use and pricing. Always check for the latest user reviews and updates, as app functionality can change over time.",
